rows.label: bf01110100_0010
rows.name:
...and that about covers it.
All right, I'll see ya later!

rows.label: bf01110100_0020
rows.name:
Should be back in a day or
two. Take it easy, Gramps!

rows.label: bf01110100_0030
rows.name:
That does not "about cover
it" in the slightest!

rows.label: bf01110100_0040
rows.name:
Why would you take a job
you know nothing about?

rows.label: bf01110100_0050
rows.name:
You don't even know
who your employer is!

rows.label: bf01110100_0060
rows.name:
This came straight from the Chairman,
remember? What more do you need?

rows.label: bf01110100_0070
rows.name:
Anyway, I'm off. You can
take a nap while you wait!

rows.label: bf01110100_0080
rows.name: H-hey! Come back here, will you?! Rex!
